        <abstract>
            <para>This dataset is a collation of ad hoc sightings and species inventories from various locations around Pembrokeshire. It includes sightings from Special Areas of Conservation (SACs), Sites of Special Scientific Interest (SSSIs), Stackpole National Nature Reserve (NNR), and county records. This data is make up of plant, insect, mammals, lichen, mammals and bird records.</para>
        </abstract>
